{"type": "article", "id": 30805, "title": "轮廓落地灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-09T23:01:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160809215600TkBXYZg7jDfCyeGp.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>初看时你很有可能觉得这个只有金属轮廓的落地灯 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41225977/Silhouette-Floor-Lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Silhouette</a> 再普通不过了。然而，只有凑近了观察你才能发现设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kevinchiam\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kevin Chiam</a> 在 LED 灯的处理上所暗藏的“小心机”：“灯罩”底部那个被圆柱穿过的平面正是它的光源所在，另一面还可以摆放植物或是装饰品。在靠近底座的地方，Chiam 还特意设计了一个用来收纳装置，让电线不再杂乱无章。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809215615VaCv6MKYiPHTorEU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809215615MyChAH0zbXwg4Vpq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160809215615wL1IaGN27tDjMFVr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080921561571LHvRSxbKaP2n9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}